\begin_layout Standard
When the band ends its maneuvers, they will 
\noun on
Lock and Close
\noun default
.
 The Lock and Close will always end a maneuver and put the performers' feet
 idle and stationary.
 It consists of two parts: the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

lock
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 and the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

close
\begin_inset Quotes erd
