\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To roll-off with the mace, raise it up in the air and hold the very bottom
 with your left hand, and grab about a foot higher with the right hand.
 Move your hands in alternating circles, effectively moving the dome of
 the mace in a large circle.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
To roll-off without the mace, point your finger in the sky and make large
 circles, making sure to have the arm bent at the elbow and moving.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
